{
  "info": {
    "name": "Sports Facility API",
    "_postman_id": "sf-api-collection-0001",
    "description": "Koleksi endpoint Sports Facility Management System (Express + Prisma + PostgreSQL).\n\nBase URL: {{base_url}} = http://localhost:3000/api/v1\n\nAlur pakai:\n1. Jalankan `npm run dev`.\n2. Auth > Register (sekali) lalu Auth > Login. Script otomatis menyimpan accessToken & refreshToken ke variable koleksi.\n3. Endpoint ber-auth otomatis memakai Bearer {{token}}.\n\nPublik (tanpa token): Health, Courts (GET), Pricing (GET), Abonemen > Packages.\nAdmin-only ditandai (admin) — perlu login akun ber-role admin/superadmin.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "auth": {
    "type": "bearer",
    "bearer": [
      {
        "key": "token",
        "value": "{{token}}",
        "type": "string"
      }
    ]
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000/api/v1",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "refresh_token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "court_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "booking_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "package_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "registration_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "payment_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "today",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
